'''SecuriTech''' was an influential vehicle manufacturing company within the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]]. SecuriTech supplied the [[Corporate Sector Authority/Legends|Corporate Sector Authority]] with patrol vehicles which included the [[Espo Walker 91]] and the [[Espo Walker 101]]. It also produced [[Gladiator walker]]s for civilians.

